To upgrade to a new upstream version:
=====================================

Tag the new version:
$ VERSION=$(date +%Y.%m.%d)
$ git tag v$VERSION

Edit debian/changelog for this new version:
$ dch --newversion $VERSION-1 

Generate a new pristine tar:
$ gbp buildpackage --git-pristine-tar --git-pristine-tar-commit --git-upstream-tag='v%(version)s' --git-ignore-new --git-no-pbuilder
